Burden of falls among people aged 60 years and older in mainland China, 
1990-2019: findings from the Global Burden of Disease Study 2019.

Ye P(1), Er Y(2), Wang H(3), Fang L(4), Li B(5), Ivers R(6), Keay L(7), Duan 
